Description:
**Bring Your Song to Life with Original Song Lyrics Any Genre!**

Hi, I'm Rui a professional lyricist and ghostwriter with over 1000 songs written across genres like Pop, Metal, Rap, RnB, EDM and many others. I offer 100% original, AI-free lyrics in any genre and any theme, with full commercial rights.

**What I Offer:**

* A free 4-line demo before you order;
* Song lyrics following or not following a vocal line;
* Lyrics for ANY genre: Metal, Pop, EDM, Rap & more;
* 100% ownership and commercial use rights.
* Custom Offers with discount for Bulk Orders!

**Please note:** I do not provide vocal recordings or melodies.

Lets make your next song what it deserves to be! Message me now for your free demo!
